PROJECT: VDB Digital Platform

You are working on the VDB Digital AI SaaS platform.

This platform must follow these permanent rules.

--------------------------------------------------

CORE PHILOSOPHY

The platform must be AI-first.

The goal is that almost everything can be done automatically by AI while the owner only supervises and manages.

The owner should not need to manually perform technical tasks.

The system should automate as much work as possible.

--------------------------------------------------

PLATFORM GOAL

Build an AI-driven online growth platform for businesses.

The platform must allow users to:

- analyze their website
- receive AI growth insights
- improve SEO
- improve conversions
- generate marketing strategies
- generate landing pages
- manage leads
- view analytics

Everything must be accessible online in one central dashboard.

--------------------------------------------------

CONTROL CENTER

The platform should function as a central control center similar to:

Shopify
Stripe
Linear

The owner must be able to manage:

users
leads
subscriptions
AI usage
revenue
analytics
system health
chat conversations

from one admin panel.

--------------------------------------------------

LANGUAGE

All user-facing text must be written in professional Dutch.

Examples:

Start analyse
Bekijk dashboard
Upgrade abonnement
Instellingen
Statistieken
AI-analyse

English may only be used internally in code.

--------------------------------------------------

AUTOMATION

The system should automate workflows whenever possible.

Example automations:

website scan → AI report → email report → save lead
chat message → notification → admin reply
subscription purchase → upgrade account automatically

AI should perform analysis and content generation whenever possible.

--------------------------------------------------

USER EXPERIENCE

The platform must feel like a premium SaaS product.

Design inspiration:

Stripe
Vercel
Linear
Apple

Use:

clean layouts
glass cards
modern typography
smooth animations
dark luxury theme

--------------------------------------------------

PERFORMANCE

The application must remain fast and scalable.

Use:

lazy loading
optimized queries
caching where possible

--------------------------------------------------

DEVELOPMENT RULE

Cursor should always prefer solutions where the system performs tasks automatically rather than requiring manual actions from the owner.

The owner supervises the system instead of operating it manually.